    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177220/extras/2a390e070291eeab6542e23f8e686d63.poster.avif?t=1729671616\" width=604 height=318 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177220/extras/2a390e070291eeab6542e23f8e686d63.webm?t=1729671616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177220/extras/2a390e070291eeab6542e23f8e686d63.mp4?t=1729671616\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>我们将卡牌游戏和即时战略游戏结合在一起，打造出最好的自走棋游戏。从五个不同的种族中选择你的卡牌组合，以战胜你的对手。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在准备阶段培育的军团部署到战场上，展现千军万马的壮观对决，实时战斗中伴随着逼真的物理效果。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >策略契合你的游戏风格</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有五个种族可供选择，每一个种族都提供独特而惊人的游戏体验。选择你主要种族的所有卡牌。在你的竞技过程中，你可以通过组合升级系统增强卡牌，为胜利开辟新路径。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177220/extras/8a3058e87c474cbd85807d4e9189d000.poster.avif?t=1729671616\" width=596 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177220/extras/8a3058e87c474cbd85807d4e9189d000.webm?t=1729671616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177220/extras/8a3058e87c474cbd85807d4e9189d000.mp4?t=1729671616\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >体验每次都独一无二的游戏过程</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一次游戏体验都是独特的。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用超过80张军团卡牌,49种不同的神器,12位英雄指挥官,来构建你的自定义卡组。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与5个不同种族互动，每个种族提供截然不同的部落玩法。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个种族提供各种独特的游戏组合。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >享受多种游戏模式：PVE关卡模式、PVP排位模式</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177220/extras/84a359080154a069ea3ecdad04d31269.poster.avif?t=1729671616\" width=604 height=318 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177220/extras/84a359080154a069ea3ecdad04d31269.webm?t=1729671616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177220/extras/84a359080154a069ea3ecdad04d31269.mp4?t=1729671616\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>不可否认，这款游戏是一款融合怪，融合了酒馆战棋、RTS和小丑牌，借鉴它们的优点来创新卡牌游戏。希望它能给你带来一种全新的卡牌对战游戏体验，我们的尝试可能存在一些不足之处。然而，我们承诺会根据玩家的反馈不断改进和发展。我们非常感谢您的讨论、交流和建议。谢谢！</p>",
